column1: Atmospheric CO2 concentrations (ppm) derived from in situ air measurements
at Mauna Loa, Observatory, Hawaii: Latitude 19.5°N Longitude 155.6°W Elevation 3397m
These data are a compilation of the latest monthly MLO data set and any weekly and
daily values past the end date of the monthly data set.
This data comes from current data analysis and are not the final data sets found on
https://scrippsco2.ucsd.edu/data/atmospheric_co2/mlo.html.
Official data sets are found at
monthly archive: https://scrippsco2.ucsd.edu/assets/data/atmospheric/stations/in_situ_co2/monthly/monthly_in_situ_co2_mlo.csv
weekly archive: https://scrippsco2.ucsd.edu/assets/data/atmospheric/stations/in_situ_co2/weekly/weekly_in_situ_co2_mlo.csv
daily archive: https://scrippsco2.ucsd.edu/assets/data/atmospheric/stations/in_situ_co2/daily/daily_in_situ_co2_mlo.csv
These data are not final because they haven't been processed to account for outliers
The archived data are subject to correction each month with the latest gas calibrations
